從來都沒懷疑過佢，點解佢要咁對我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb30a388ca4adadbcac3bd93b31f1d4cb2a96f4","tid":249831,"uid":79296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:09:09.000Z","msg":"你平時係咪好chur果d?"},{"pid":"1d88a502947c8582c56ad8acf7901b34adafa74f","tid":249831,"uid":106583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你平時係咪好chur果d?</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n佢上堂，同朋友出街，都唔會chur佢whatsapp/電話<br />\n<br />\n（佢可以灰剔我/藍剔我，但我就唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n佢想打機咪陪佢打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6596ec8ee8f47353d78a1126ea320dee7276b4","tid":249831,"uid":30395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:59:58.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"7d581d82f4a85fe9dafde95bc74bc9474a91e1cb","tid":249831,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T21:02:52.000Z","msg":"一睇就知遲早會帽<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己同其他男仔出街無問題<br />\n如果條仔進取少少<br />\n一個唔覺意去個無人地方<br />\n錫兩錫已經可以..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己諗"},{"pid":"fecf5864c1c2ee2bf9a439774434073f26e54537","tid":249831,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T21:21:41.000Z","msg":"9個月呃咗4次<br />\n<br />\n無謂嘥時間啦"},{"pid":"8b59f63d8e83387656476b6582a1adb8b9a5d1ee","tid":249831,"uid":106583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T21:30:04.000Z","msg":"到依家都訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人真係一樣好中意講大話既生物<br />\n依家我信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc086296a5f49272b211bd0082d3d23fff8686f5","tid":249831,"uid":113034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T21:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到依家都訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 